{"tid":1365403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"孫楊條禁藥撚，好撚串！","createTime":"2019-07-25T15:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T16:06:40.000Z","uid":175258,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fd2278ed2938751c97e681cb7fbb31030749699b","tid":1365403,"uid":175258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2570544409699243&amp;id=317278538359186\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2570544409699243%26id%3D317278538359186&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=bd1e7920\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2570544409699243&amp;id=317278538359186</a>"},{"pid":"13ce78a2d76063b90094c371c186d4c90fdf41b0","tid":1365403,"uid":48286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:35:44.000Z","msg":"尿紫楊丫嘛<br />\n聽過下"},{"pid":"b400967d7fbf2f8815d9f34d74b6c93c2f970a3e","tid":1365403,"uid":175258,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iUh1uHb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiUh1uHb.jpg&h=43ce86fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T3BE0OS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT3BE0OS.jpg&h=189c57b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5298d04c9a29fa91df6e78ed6097d3e28e3a386e","tid":1365403,"uid":175258,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:38:20.000Z","msg":"【孫揚：你是輸家 我是贏家  BCC抨擊「行為醜陋」】<br />\n<br />\n身陷藥檢風波的中國泳手孫揚，出戰於韓國光州舉行的2019年世界游泳錦標賽。由於禁藥疑雲未解，藥檢事件尚待運動仲裁庭於9月開庭，孫揚遭到部分選手抵制。<br />\n<br />\n昨日舉行200公尺自由式決賽，並列第3的英國泳手Duncan Scott，響應澳洲泳手賀頓(Mack Horton)，拒絕與獲得金牌的孫揚合照。<br />\n<br />\n孫揚於領獎下台後，回頭找Scott，指著他說：「You're a loser, I'm a winner （你是輸家，我是贏家）」。一切被在場攝影師拍下，BBC點名指孫揚「ugly（行為醜陋）」。"},{"pid":"9b88272ddd91a156ea2c2d5cc6cd2158de4c5a63","tid":1365403,"uid":143582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:02:11.000Z","msg":"幾時收皮"},{"pid":"2db92eae21748a30d5a9a82bd8ff05162eec4bdb","tid":1365403,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:03:10.000Z","msg":"支那種"},{"pid":"eeec860027160a2ef21697e79df8aca587a98a7f","tid":1365403,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6iPjgvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6iPjgvY.jpg&h=fb27b267&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72206d4b27599d5a284b2971322e09ddbae58695","tid":1365403,"uid":224453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:04:23.000Z","msg":"上次唔係已經驗過之後唔俾再參賽？"},{"pid":"fdd61cd820e858bf3d90cfeb26765504ea8d4f9c","tid":1365403,"uid":177856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:04:32.000Z","msg":"食咁撚多藥，肯定早死！過多四十歲先講嘢！"},{"pid":"b69866edb5fb32b7bf18dc46bb6109fc4075245f","tid":1365403,"uid":140738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:05:23.000Z","msg":"支那人係咁上下<br />\n<br />\n唔係咩新聞黎"},{"pid":"1d062c2b8f3932c860824cacf7870239c745a9c0","tid":1365403,"uid":218028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:05:55.000Z","msg":"連澳洲人都知 唉"},{"pid":"a91793d2ad8559f68a49b4e1eee9c03069f8777d","tid":1365403,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:06:40.000Z","msg":"堂堂中国人居然要用洋鬼子的語言<br />\n簡直有辱國體<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}